<div type="edition" xml:lang="tam-Latn" rendition="class:tamil maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/><hi rend="grantha">svasti śrī</hi> <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> komāṟapaṉmarāṉa tiripuvaṉaccakkaravattika <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> koṇṭaruḷiya cuntarapāṇṭiyatevaṟku <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> paṭiye kaṭamai Iṟukkumpaṭi peṟaveṇume <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="2"/>kum coṉakaṟkum civitamāka Aṭaitta nāḷil taraṅ kulai <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> m taṇṭiṉārākavum paṇṭu Iṟuttuvanta tara <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> tam ceytaruḷivanta tirumukappaṭi Irupatto <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="3"/><unclear>n</unclear>āṇūṟṟiṉāl miṉavataraiyar Eḷuttiṉālum vayalnā <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> rayar Eḷuttiṉālum pallavarā<hi rend="grantha">ja</hi>ṉ Eḻuttiṉālum <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> nellu Aiyṅkalaṉe Irutūṇip patakku Irunāḻi <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="4"/>n tarattukku māttāl nellu Eḷukalaṉe Irutūṇik kuṟuṇi nāṉāḻi <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> m kācu Aṟumāvarai muntirikaiyum muṉṟān tarattukkum <gap reason="lost" quantity="4" unit="character"/> rumāvukku kācu Uṭppaṭa nāṟkala nellu I <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="5"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> nilam payirpāṟttu payir nilainiṉṟa ni <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="6" unit="character"/> ṭai Ācāriya<supplied reason="omitted">ṉ</supplied> Eḻuttu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g>
</p>

